title: Digit humanoid joins Mercado Libre warehouse
description:
Partnership will integrate Digit robots into fulfillment operations beginning in Texas, with future expansion capabilities for Latin America.

The post Digit humanoid joins Mercado Libre warehouse appeared first on The Robot Report.
